-05T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"我相信支簽系香港會走向一個好的新局面，登基死傷難免<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4b47348ef8292db9a3c94c53fb62b89454b043","tid":1769851,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}